Barrelstalk is a fungus that grows in the Underdark, named for its barrel-like shape. When it's young, barrelstalk can be used in a variety of recipes! If allowed to mature, it can be as hard as wood - and comes with spores that make it inedible.

((This is a Job System Item.))
